headline: Berlin Heals Welcomes Rob ten Hoedt as New Chairman of the Board
summary: Berlin Heals Holding AG (Zug, Switzerland) is pleased to announce the appointment of Rob ten Hoedt as the new Chairman of the Board of Directors.

headline: How Recent Developments Are Shaping the Medtronic Investment Story
summary: Medtronic's fair value estimate has nudged higher to $111.05 from $109.82 as analysts grow more confident that the company can sustain mid single digit plus organic growth. A slightly lower discount rate and largely unchanged revenue growth outlook reflect a market that is increasingly willing to recognize the durability of Medtronic's cash flow narrative, while still acknowledging execution risks.
